#: lib/retro_hex_chat/commands/handlers/mode.ex:37
#: lib/retro_hex_chat/commands/handlers/mode.ex:99
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Change channel settings and user privileges using mode flags.\n"
"Flags: +o (operator), +v (voice), +b (ban), +h (half-op), +m (moderated), +i (invite-only), +t (topic protected), +k (key/password), +l (user limit), +n (no external messages), +j (join throttle), +K (no knock).\n"
"Requires: channel operator. Half-operators can only set +v/-v. Must be in a channel."
msgstr ""
"Cambiar configuración del canal y privilegios del usuario usando banderas de modo.\n"
"Banderas: +o (operador), +v (voz), +b (ban), +h (half-op), +m (moderado), +i (invitado solo), +t (topic protected), +k (key/password), +l (usuario límite), +n (no mensajes externos), +j (juego acelerado), +K (no golpe).\n"
"Requiere: operador de canal. Media-operadores sólo pueden establecer +v/-v. Debe estar en un canal."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/commands/handlers/nick.ex:82
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Change your display name in the chat. A confirmation dialog appears before "
"the change takes effect."
